PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,FUK police will only have three
OL,8,Fofficers in the US at the upcoming
OL,9,FWorld Cup because American authorities
OL,10,Fhave refused to foot the bill.
OL,12,FThis number compares to 40 who
OL,13,Fattended the Euros tournament in
OL,14,FGermany ` all paid for by the hosts.
OL,16,FWhile UK police personnel overseas
OL,17,Fhave no legal powers, they act as a
OL,18,Fuseful conduit between fans and local
OL,19,Flaw enforcement agencies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,FIn the USA, it's predicted that up to
OL,8,F15,000 England fans could attend each
OL,9,Fgroup game involving Thomas Tuchel's
OL,10,Fteam, which equates to one officer for
OL,11,Fevery 5,000 supporters.
OL,13,FWhile England fan behaviour has been
OL,14,Fgenerally very good at recent major
OL,15,Ftournaments, the travelling police
OL,16,Fteam have acted as a vital go-between,
OL,17,Fexplaining to local law agencies that
OL,18,Ftheir 'boisterous' behaviour is all in
OL,19,Fgood spirits, and not a precursor to
OL,20,Fany violent incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,FFewer officers on the ground increases
OL,8,Fthe risk that the message does not get
OL,9,Fthrough.
OL,11,FAsked why so few British officers are
OL,12,Fbeing sent, the National Police
OL,13,FChiefs' Council (NPCC) lead for
OL,14,Ffootball policing, Chief Constable
OL,15,FMark Roberts, said it was down to the
OL,16,Fhost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,F"They decide whether or not they want
OL,8,Fmobile teams... that's entirely within
OL,9,Ftheir gift. We're sending them because
OL,10,Fwe see the benefit of it and we want
OL,11,Fthat presence on the ground."
OL,13,FChief Constable Roberts said asking
OL,14,Fthe Westminster government for more
OL,15,Ffunding would have been a "non-
OL,16,Fstarter" due to existing budget cuts
OL,17,Fto policing at home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,F"We're funding it because we want our
OL,8,Fpeople out there to brief local law
OL,9,Fenforcement so they have an accurate
OL,10,Fimpression of our people," he said.
OL,12,F"You will know there's a hangover from
OL,13,Fprevious poor behaviour going back to
OL,14,Fthe 80s that's really difficult to
OL,15,Fshake. So we want to make sure that
OL,16,Four fans are judged and dealt with on
OL,17,Fthe basis of behaviour, not
OL,18,Fmisconceptions."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,FChief Constable Roberts accepted that
OL,8,Fthere is always a risk of police
OL,9,Foverreacting to rowdy fans but said he
OL,10,Fhas been encouraged by outcomes at
OL,11,Frecent tournaments.
OL,13,F"We thought there was that risk in
OL,14,FQatar, and it didn't transpire. So I'm
OL,15,Fencouraged by what I've seen so far
OL,16,Fabout the willingness to understand
OL,17,Fit's different.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,F"We'll do our bit. The best antidote
OL,8,Fto all of this is for fans to be aware
OL,9,Fthey're in different surroundings ` by
OL,10,Fall means, have a drink, but not to
OL,11,Fexcess, because we know that when
OL,12,Fpeople drink to excess, then sometimes
OL,13,Freason goes out the window. Just be
OL,14,Fsensible, have a great time."
OL,16,FThe Football Supporters Association
OL,17,Fwill be putting together a glossary of
OL,18,Fadvice for travelling fans, alerting
OL,19,Fthem to travel issues and local laws,
OL,20,Fwhich change country by country and
OL,21,Fstate by state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,FIn Texas, not even passengers are
OL,8,Fallowed to drink alcohol in a car, for
OL,9,Fexample, whereas in Mexico, vapes are
OL,10,Fbanned.
OL,12,FBack in the UK, police will be keeping
OL,13,Fa close eye on online abuse, which
OL,14,Fgenerally increases during major
OL,15,Ftournaments.
OL,17,FIncidents are increasing, particularly
OL,18,Fof racial abuse, and they are ready to
OL,19,Ftrack down and charge anyone who posts
OL,20,Fmalicious or offensive content.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,FAsked how he feels about the prospect
OL,8,Fof American-style policing during the
OL,9,Ftournament, Thomas Concannon, Premier
OL,10,FLeague Network Manager for the
OL,11,FFootball Supporters' Association, did
OL,12,Fnot appear too concerned.
OL,14,F"They're used to dealing with large
OL,15,Fsporting events and, you know,
OL,16,Fthousands of fans travelling to events
OL,17,Fand things like that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779437195
OL,3,CWorld Cup: US won't pay for UK police
OL,4,Cas three officers deployed for 40,000
OL,5,Cfans
OL,7,F"So I think there's no major concern
OL,8,Fon that front. England fans are used
OL,9,Fto travelling all around the world and
OL,10,Fdealing with local, different local
OL,11,Flaws and customs, and I'm sure that
OL,12,Fwon't be any different."
